#: .\dreams.json
msgid "You have an odd dream about tortoises."
msgstr "你做了一个关于乌龟的怪梦。"

#: .\dreams.json
msgid "Your dreams give you a strange protected feeling."
msgstr "你的梦境赋予你一种奇特的受保护感。"

#: .\dreams.json
msgid "You have a strange dream of retreating into a shell and staying there."
msgstr "你做了一个怪梦，梦见自己缩进壳里并待在那儿。"

#: .\dreams.json
msgid ""
"In your dream, you catch a distinctively tortoise-like image of yourself."
msgstr "在你的梦中，你捕捉到一个明显像乌龟般的自我形象。"

#: .\dreams.json
msgid ""
"You are comforted by a dream of you being protected by your strong shell as "
"predators try in vain to eat you."
msgstr "你梦见自己受到坚硬外壳的保护，捕食者徒劳地试图吃掉你，这让你感到安慰。"

#: .\dreams.json
msgid ""
"You find it hard to wake from your peaceful dream of basking in the sun."
msgstr "你发现自己很难从那个在阳光下晒太阳的宁静梦境中醒来。"

#: .\dreams.json
msgid ""
"You feel safe knowing that no matter how fast everything else may be, your "
"shell will protect you."
msgstr "你知道无论其他事物有多快，你的外壳都会保护你，这让你感到安全。"

#: .\dreams.json
msgid "You have a long life ahead of you. Time to take it slow."
msgstr "你面前还有漫长的人生。是时候放慢脚步了。"

#: .\modinfo.json
msgid "Mutation Changes Snofielf"
msgstr "突变调整 Snofielf"

#. ~ Description for Mutation Changes Snofielf
#: .\modinfo.json
msgid ""
"Changes, rebalances and adds some more mutations. This a fixed version for "
"the fixed version to cleanse the mod of even more old bugs and problems. It "
"also has some new mutations and additions."
msgstr "调整、重新平衡并添加更多突变。这是修复版本的修复版，旨在清除模组中更多旧有错误和问题。它还包含一些新的突变和补充内容。"

#: .\mutagen.json
msgid "tortoise serum"
msgid_plural "tortoise serums"
msgstr[0] "乌龟血清"

#: .\mutagen.json
msgid "tortoise mutagen"
msgid_plural "tortoise mutagens"
msgstr[0] "乌龟诱变剂"

#. ~ Mutation class name
#: .\mutation_category.json .\mutations.json
msgid "Tortoise"
msgstr "乌龟"

#. ~ Mutation class: Tortoise mutagen_message
#: .\mutation_category.json
msgid "You feel like everything is happening too quickly."
msgstr "你觉得一切都发生得太快了。"

#. ~ Mutation class: Tortoise iv_message
#: .\mutation_category.json
msgid "Everything slows down for just a moment."
msgstr "一切都在瞬间慢了下来。"

#. ~ Mutation class: Tortoise Male memorial messsage
#: .\mutation_category.json
msgctxt "memorial_male"
msgid "Became tortoisey enough for the tortoise club."
msgstr "变得足够龟化，足以加入乌龟俱乐部。"

#. ~ Mutation class: Tortoise Female memorial messsage
#: .\mutation_category.json
msgctxt "memorial_female"
msgid "Became tortoisey enough for the tortoise club."
msgstr "变得足够龟化，足以加入乌龟俱乐部。"

#. ~ Mutation class name
#: .\mutation_category.json
msgid "Chimera"
msgstr "奇美拉"

#. ~ Mutation class: Chimera mutagen_message
#: .\mutation_category.json
msgid "You need to roar, bask, bite, and flap.  NOW!."
msgstr "你需要咆哮、晒太阳、撕咬和拍打翅膀。现在！"

#. ~ Mutation class: Chimera iv_message
#: .\mutation_category.json
msgid "Every animal that ever lived... bursting! From! YOU!"
msgstr "所有曾经存在的动物……从你体内迸发而出！"

#. ~ Mutation class: Chimera iv_sleep_message
#: .\mutation_category.json
msgid "With a final *pop*, you go out like a light...."
msgstr "随着最后一声*噗*，你像灯一样熄灭了……"

#. ~ Mutation class: Chimera iv_sound_message
#: .\mutation_category.json
msgid "You roar in agony!!"
msgstr "你痛苦地咆哮！！"

#. ~ Mutation class: Chimera Male memorial messsage
#: .\mutation_category.json
msgctxt "memorial_male"
msgid "United disunity."
msgstr "统一的分裂。"

#. ~ Mutation class: Chimera Female memorial messsage
#: .\mutation_category.json
msgctxt "memorial_female"
msgid "United disunity."
msgstr "统一的分裂。"

#: .\mutations.json
msgid "Animal Skin"
msgstr "动物皮肤"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Animal Skin'}
#: .\mutations.json
msgid ""
"Your skin has mutated noticeably because it is more related to animals than "
"humans. It grows more hair than a human skin and its a bit tougher, and "
"doesn't seem to  protect you from cold... Beasty! But you are doing just "
"fine. Also you won't have any problem related to skin."
msgstr ""
"你的皮肤发生了显著变异，因为它与动物的关联性比人类更强。它比人类皮肤长出更多毛发，也更为坚韧，但似乎并不能保护你免受寒冷……真是野兽般！不过你感觉还好。此外，你不会遇到任何与皮肤相关的问题。"

#: .\mutations.json
msgid "Avian Skin"
msgstr "鸟类皮肤"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Avian Skin'}
#: .\mutations.json
msgid ""
"Your skin has mutated noticeably because it is more related to birds than "
"humans. At the beggining it looks normal but if you look closely, it looks "
"like if you are having a classic 'chicken skin' symptom just that is a "
"little more scaly, a bit pinkier, and it is a bit more delicate... Birdie! "
"But you are doing just fine. Also you won't have any problem related to "
"skin."
msgstr ""
"你的皮肤发生了显著变异，因为它与鸟类的关联性比人类更强。起初看起来正常，但仔细观察，就像患上了典型的“鸡皮疙瘩”症状，只是鳞片更多、略带粉红，且更为娇嫩……像小鸟一样！不过你感觉还好。此外，你不会遇到任何与皮肤相关的问题。"

#: .\mutations.json
msgid "Snake Skin"
msgstr "蛇类皮肤"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Snake Skin'}
#: .\mutations.json
msgid ""
"Your skin has mutated noticeably because it is more related to reptiles than"
" humans. It has a very scaly texture, its a bit shiny, a bit more hardy, and"
" a little slippery. Or similar to that of snakes for short... Snakey! But "
"you are doing just fine. Also you won't have any problem related to skin."
msgstr ""
"你的皮肤发生了显著变异，因为它与爬行动物的关联性比人类更强。它具有非常鳞片状的纹理，略带光泽，更为坚韧，且有些滑腻。简而言之，类似于蛇皮……像蛇一样！不过你感觉还好。此外，你不会遇到任何与皮肤相关的问题。"

#: .\mutations.json
msgid "Tortoise Tail"
msgstr "龟类尾巴"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Tortoise Tail'}
#: .\mutations.json
msgid ""
"You grown a short, thin tail. It looks cute and quite tortoisey, but it "
"otherwise serves no purpose."
msgstr "你长出了一条短而细的尾巴。它看起来很可爱，颇有龟类特征，但除此之外并无实际用途。"

#. ~ Description for WEB_SPINNER
#: .\mutations.json
msgid ""
"You have grown a spider abdomen that produces and anchors webbing.  Too bad "
"you can't seem to control the process.  There is a chance that you will "
"leave webs in your wake. Prevents wearing non-fabric pants"
msgstr "你长出了一个蜘蛛腹部，能够产生并固定蛛网。可惜你似乎无法控制这个过程。你有可能会在身后留下蛛网。无法穿着非织物裤子。"

#: .\mutations.json
msgid "Avian Physique"
msgstr "鸟类体格"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Avian Physique'}
#: .\mutations.json
msgid ""
"Your physiology now has more in common with birds than it does humans. The "
"scales on your arms and legs provide some protection and the talons on your "
"feet leave a nasty scratch, but your changed feet prevents you from wearing "
"footgear. +2 dex"
msgstr "你的生理结构现在与鸟类的共同点多于人类。手臂和腿部的鳞片提供了一些保护，脚上的利爪能造成严重的抓伤，但变异的脚部使你无法穿鞋。+2 敏捷"

#: .\mutations.json
msgid "You scratch and slash at %s with the claws on your feet"
msgstr "你用脚上的爪子抓挠并撕扯 %s"

#: .\mutations.json
msgid "%1$s scratches and slashes at %2$s with the claws on their feet"
msgstr "%1$s 用脚上的爪子抓挠并撕扯 %2$s"

#: .\mutations.json
msgid "Ursine Anatomy"
msgstr "熊类解剖结构"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Ursine Anatomy'}
#: .\mutations.json
msgid ""
"Your body structure and physiology has taken on a rather ursine quality. You"
" feel a little stronger, but you look rather inhuman because of it."
msgstr "你的身体结构和生理特征呈现出相当熊类的特质。你感觉更强壮了一些，但也因此看起来相当非人。"

#: .\mutations.json
msgid "Bovine Anatomy"
msgstr "牛类解剖结构"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Bovine Anatomy'}
#: .\mutations.json
msgid ""
"Your body structure and physiology has taken on a rather bovine quality. You"
" feel a little stronger, but you look rather inhuman because of it."
msgstr "你的身体结构和生理特征呈现出相当牛类的特质。你感觉更强壮了一些，但也因此看起来相当非人。"

#: .\mutations.json
msgid "Tortoise Anatomy"
msgstr "龟类解剖结构"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Tortoise Anatomy'}
#: .\mutations.json
msgid ""
"Your body structure and physiology has taken on a rather tortoisey quality. "
"You feel a little stronger and safer, but you look rather inhuman because of"
" it."
msgstr "你的身体结构和生理特征呈现出相当龟类的特质。你感觉更强壮、更安全了一些，但也因此看起来相当非人。"

#: .\mutations.json
msgid "Raptor Anatomy"
msgstr "猛禽解剖结构"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Raptor Anatomy'}
#: .\mutations.json
msgid ""
"Your body structure and physiology has become similar to that of a "
"velociraptor. You feel a little stronger and faster, but you look rather "
"inhuman because of it."
msgstr "你的身体结构和生理特征变得类似于迅猛龙。你感觉更强壮、更快速了一些，但也因此看起来相当非人。"

#: .\mutations.json
msgid "Flora"
msgstr "植物体"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Flora'}
#: .\mutations.json
msgid ""
"The structure of your body and your internal physiology has more in common "
"with flora than it does fauna. Why bother with things like 'scavenging' and "
"'hunting' when there is good soil to plant yourself in?."
msgstr "你的身体结构和内部生理特征与植物的共同点多于动物。当有肥沃的土壤可以扎根时，何必费心于“拾荒”和“狩猎”这类事情呢？"

#: .\mutations.json
msgid "Chimerical Anatomy"
msgstr "嵌合体解剖结构"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Chimerical Anatomy'}
#: .\mutations.json
msgid ""
"Your body structure and physiology has become an amalgamation of multiple "
"different animals. You feel unstoppable, but you now no longer even look "
"vaguely human. Any potential meal looking at you would have no doubt that "
"you are some sort of chimerical monster."
msgstr ""
"你的身体结构和生理特征变成了多种不同动物的混合体。你感觉势不可挡，但你现在甚至不再有丝毫人形。任何潜在的猎物看到你都会毫无疑问地认为你是某种嵌合怪物。"

#: .\mutations.json
msgid "Beastly Anatomy"
msgstr "野兽解剖结构"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Beastly Anatomy'}
#: .\mutations.json
msgid ""
"Your body structure and physiology has become that of some super predatory "
"beast. You have never felt better, but there would be little doubt in "
"anyone's mind that you are anything but human."
msgstr "你的身体结构和生理特征变成了某种超级掠食性野兽的模样。你从未感觉如此之好，但任何人都会毫无疑问地认为你绝非人类。"

#: .\mutations.json
msgid "Lupine Anatomy"
msgstr "狼类解剖结构"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Lupine Anatomy'}
#: .\mutations.json
msgid ""
"Your body structure and physiology has more in common with canines than it "
"does humans. You feel like a fearless predator, but you bet people would "
"mistake you for a werewolf."
msgstr "你的身体结构与生理特征与犬类更为相似，而非人类。你感觉自己像一头无畏的掠食者，但打赌人们会把你误认为狼人。"

#: .\mutations.json
msgid "Feline Anatomy"
msgstr "猫科解剖结构"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Feline Anatomy'}
#: .\mutations.json
msgid ""
"Your body structure and physiology has more in common with felines than it "
"does humans. You feel as nimble as a cat, but no one would mistake you for "
"human anymore."
msgstr "你的身体结构与生理特征与猫科动物更为相似，而非人类。你感觉像猫一样敏捷，但再也不会有人把你误认为人类了。"

#: .\mutations.json
msgid "Fish Anatomy"
msgstr "鱼类解剖结构"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Fish Anatomy'}
#: .\mutations.json
msgid ""
"Your body structure and physiology has become similar to that of some "
"aquatic animal. You feel faster than before, but you look very inhuman "
"because of it. All you want to do is get back into the water."
msgstr "你的身体结构与生理特征变得类似于某些水生动物。你感觉比以前更快了，但因此看起来非常不像人类。你只想回到水里去。"

#: .\mutations.json
msgid "Reptilian Anatomy"
msgstr "爬行类解剖结构"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Reptilian Anatomy'}
#: .\mutations.json
msgid ""
"Your body structure and physiology has more in common with crocodilians than"
" of humans. Your muscles bulge with power, but no one would mistake you for "
"human. Maybe you should find a nice sunny spot to bask in."
msgstr ""
"你的身体结构与生理特征与鳄鱼类更为相似，而非人类。你的肌肉因力量而膨胀，但再也不会有人把你误认为人类了。也许你该找个阳光充足的地方晒晒太阳。"

#: .\mutations.json
msgid "Rodentine Anatomy"
msgstr "啮齿类解剖结构"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Rodentine Anatomy'}
#: .\mutations.json
msgid ""
"You don't have time for lollygagging when there's survival at stake. Who "
"cares that you're not even human anymore when the other survivors out there "
"can't even compete with you?"
msgstr "当生存岌岌可危时，你没时间闲逛。当其他幸存者甚至无法与你竞争时，谁还在乎你已不再是人？"

#: .\mutations.json
msgid "Arachnid Anatomy"
msgstr "蛛形纲解剖结构"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Arachnid Anatomy'}
#: .\mutations.json
msgid ""
"Your body structure and physiology has more in common with arachnids than of"
" humans. Your arachnid abdomen now safely houses your vital organs. You "
"wonder what will wander into your web today."
msgstr "你的身体结构与生理特征与蛛形纲动物更为相似，而非人类。你的蛛形腹部现在安全地容纳着你的重要器官。你想知道今天会有什么东西闯入你的网中。"

#: .\mutations.json
msgid "Insectile Anatomy"
msgstr "昆虫类解剖结构"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Insectile Anatomy'}
#: .\mutations.json
msgid ""
"Your body structure and physiology has more in common with insects than of "
"humans. Your insectile abdomen now safely houses your vital organs, but you "
"doubt that you will be making any human friends soon."
msgstr "你的身体结构与生理特征与昆虫更为相似，而非人类。你的昆虫腹部现在安全地容纳着你的重要器官，但你怀疑自己很快就能交到人类朋友。"

#: .\mutations.json
msgid "Blossomed"
msgstr "开花"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Blossomed'}
#: .\mutations.json
msgid ""
"Your entire head has become a flower with a deadly stinger in its center "
"much like like those triffids that you saw earlier. You can still eat, "
"breathe, and see just fine, but you cannot wear anything on or around your "
"head."
msgstr ""
"你的整个头部变成了一朵花，花心有一根致命的刺，就像你之前看到的那些三裂植物一样。你仍然可以正常进食、呼吸和视物，但无法在头部或周围穿戴任何东西。"

#: .\mutations.json
msgid "You stab at %s with the stinger inside your petals"
msgstr "你用花瓣内的刺刺向%s"

#: .\mutations.json
msgid "%1$s stabs at %2$s with the stinger inside their petals"
msgstr "%1$s用他们花瓣内的刺刺向%2$s"

#: .\mutations.json
msgid "Mossy"
msgstr "苔藓覆盖"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Mossy'}
#: .\mutations.json
msgid ""
"A deep green moss has grown a patchy covering over parts of your body "
"providing some protection from the cold."
msgstr "深绿色的苔藓在你身体的部分区域形成了斑驳的覆盖层，提供了一些抵御寒冷的保护。"

#: .\mutations.json
msgid "Chimerical Legs"
msgstr "嵌合体腿部"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Chimerical Legs'}
#: .\mutations.json
msgid ""
"Your legs have mutated in such a manner that your body managed to develop "
"fearsome but impressive and very powerful and sharp hoof-claws, something "
"that was never seen before in the animal kingdom. They allow you to make "
"some powerful kicking attacks, but they prevent you from wearing any "
"footgear"
msgstr ""
"你的腿部发生了突变，身体成功进化出了可怕但令人印象深刻、非常强大且锋利的蹄爪，这在动物界前所未见。它们让你能进行一些强有力的踢击攻击，但也使你无法穿戴任何足部装备。"

#: .\mutations.json
msgid "You kick at %s with your hoof"
msgstr "你用蹄子踢向%s"

#: .\mutations.json
msgid "%1$s kicks at %2$s with their hoof"
msgstr "%1$s用他们的蹄子踢向%2$s"

#: .\mutations.json
msgid "You slash at %s with your claw"
msgstr "你用爪子抓向%s"

#: .\mutations.json
msgid "%1$s slashes at %2$s with their claw"
msgstr "%1$s用他们的爪子抓向%2$s"

#: .\mutations.json
msgid "Bear Feet"
msgstr "熊足"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Bear Feet'}
#: .\mutations.json
msgid ""
"Your feet have taken on a distinctly ursine quality to them.  This has no "
"effect."
msgstr "你的双脚呈现出明显的熊类特征。这没有效果。"

#: .\mutations.json
msgid "Bovine Tongue"
msgstr "牛舌"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Bovine Tongue'}
#: .\mutations.json
msgid ""
"Your tongue has flattened and has become wider, looking like that of a "
"bovine.  This has no effect."
msgstr "你的舌头变平变宽，看起来像牛舌一样。这没有效果。"

#: .\mutations.json
msgid "Ursine Tongue"
msgstr "熊舌"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Ursine Tongue'}
#: .\mutations.json
msgid ""
"Your tongue has flattened and has become longer, looking like that of a "
"bear.  This has no effect."
msgstr "你的舌头变得扁平且更长，看起来像熊的舌头。这没有效果。"

#: .\mutations.json
msgid "Tortoise Tongue"
msgstr "龟舌"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Tortoise Tongue'}
#: .\mutations.json
msgid ""
"Your tongue has become rounded and thicker, looking like that of a tortoise."
"  This has no effect."
msgstr "你的舌头变得圆润且更厚，看起来像乌龟的舌头。这没有效果。"

#: .\mutations.json
msgid "Raptor Scales"
msgstr "猛禽鳞片"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Raptor Scales'}
#: .\mutations.json
msgid ""
"A set of flexible iridescent scales has grown to cover your body, acting as "
"natural armor.  Somewhat reduces wet effects."
msgstr "一套灵活的虹彩鳞片覆盖了你的身体，充当天然护甲。略微减少潮湿效果。"

#: .\mutations.json
msgid "Raptor Feathers"
msgstr "猛禽羽毛"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Raptor Feathers'}
#: .\mutations.json
msgid ""
"A set of beautiful colored shiny feathers has grown to cover some parts of "
"your body, acting as natural armor. And making your appereance more majestic"
" than before, with a collar of feathers around your neck, that looks like a "
"crown-like set of feathers you sure, have become a presence to behold. "
"Somewhat reduces wet effects and protects slightly agaisnt cold."
msgstr ""
"一套美丽的彩色闪亮羽毛覆盖了你身体的部分区域，充当天然护甲。并使你的外观比以往更加威严，颈部周围有一圈羽毛，看起来像一顶王冠般的羽毛，你确实已成为一道值得注目的风景。略微减少潮湿效果并轻微抵御寒冷。"

#: .\mutations.json
msgid "Rough Fur"
msgstr "粗糙皮毛"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Rough Fur'}
#: .\mutations.json
msgid ""
"The on your body fur has taken on a rough texture. It provides marginal "
"protection against attacks, and considerable protection from cold."
msgstr "你身上的皮毛变得粗糙。它提供微弱的攻击防护，以及可观的寒冷防护。"

#: .\mutations.json
msgid "Thick Fur"
msgstr "厚实皮毛"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Thick Fur'}
#: .\mutations.json
msgid ""
"You've grown a thick pelt of rough black fur, providing protection from cold"
" and attacks."
msgstr "你长出了一层厚厚的粗糙黑色皮毛，提供寒冷和攻击防护。"

#: .\mutations.json
msgid "Aquatic Adaptation"
msgstr "水生适应"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Aquatic Adaptation'}
#: .\mutations.json
msgid ""
"Your body's physiology has completely adapted to life underwater. This "
"doesn't change your appearance much, but you seem to always have a fishy "
"sheen to your body.  Greatly increases wet benefits."
msgstr "你的身体生理已完全适应水下生活。这不会显著改变你的外观，但你的身体似乎总是带有鱼腥光泽。大幅增加潮湿益处。"

#: .\mutations.json
msgid "Chimerical Protection"
msgstr "奇美拉防护"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Chimerical Protection'}
#: .\mutations.json
msgid ""
"Finally! That weird skin has now developed a cohesive fur-scale skin that "
"was before unseen in the animal kingdom. This provides considerable "
"protection and warmth. Moderately reduces wet effects."
msgstr "终于！那奇怪的皮肤现在发展出一种在动物王国中前所未见的、具有凝聚力的毛鳞皮肤。这提供了可观的防护和温暖。适度减少潮湿效果。"

#: .\mutations.json
msgid "Raptor Muzzle"
msgstr "猛禽口鼻"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Raptor Muzzle'}
#: .\mutations.json
msgid ""
"Your face and jaws have extended outwards causing you to resemble an extinct"
" dinosaur. It's filled with razor sharp teeth that leave nasty wounds, but "
"it prevents you from wearing mouthgear."
msgstr "你的脸和下巴向外延伸，使你看起来像一只已灭绝的恐龙。它充满了锋利的牙齿，会造成严重的伤口，但阻止你佩戴口部装备。"

#: .\mutations.json
msgid "Beastly Muzzle"
msgstr "野兽口鼻"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Beastly Muzzle'}
#: .\mutations.json
msgid ""
"Your jaw and nose have extended into some kind of monstrous muzzle. It "
"delivers a strong bite and looks absolutely beastly, but prevents you from "
"wearing mouthgear."
msgstr "你的下巴和鼻子延伸成某种怪物般的口鼻。它能进行强力撕咬，看起来绝对野兽，但阻止你佩戴口部装备。"

#: .\mutations.json
msgid "You chomp %s"
msgstr "你猛咬 %s"

#: .\mutations.json
msgid "%1$s chomps %2$s"
msgstr "%1$s 猛咬 %2$s"

#: .\mutations.json
msgid "Chimerical Muzzle"
msgstr "奇美拉口鼻"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Chimerical Muzzle'}
#: .\mutations.json
msgid ""
"Your face and jaws have extended outwards into some sort of bizarre muzzle "
"that blends features from various animals. You could not even begin to guess"
" what it could belong to, but you do know that it has one powerful bite."
msgstr "你的脸和下巴向外延伸成某种奇异的、融合了多种动物特征的口鼻。你甚至无法猜测它可能属于什么生物，但你知道它确实具有强大的咬合力。"

#: .\mutations.json
msgid "You bite and rend %s"
msgstr "你撕咬并撕裂 %s"

#: .\mutations.json
msgid "%1$s bites and rends %2$s"
msgstr "%1$s 撕咬并撕裂 %2$s"

#. ~ Description for LARGE
#: .\mutations.json
msgid ""
"You have grown noticeably taller and broader.  Much of it is useful muscle "
"mass (Strength +3), but you find it throws off your balance and you get in "
"your own way (+10 torso and arm encumbrance)."
msgstr "你明显变得更高更壮。其中大部分是有用的肌肉量（力量 +3），但你发现这会影响你的平衡，并让你自己碍手碍脚（躯干和手臂负重 +10）。"

#. ~ Description for LARGE_OK
#: .\mutations.json
msgid "You carry your rugged body with the dignity you deserve.  Strength +4."
msgstr "你以应得的尊严承载着你粗犷的身体。力量 +4。"

#. ~ Description for HUGE
#: .\mutations.json
msgid ""
"You have grown even more massive, to the point where you cannot usefully fit"
" into human-sized clothing or vehicles.  Much of it is powerful muscle mass "
"(Strength +6), but it's a real pain to haul around."
msgstr "你变得更加庞大，以至于无法有效穿上人类尺寸的衣物或进入车辆。其中大部分是强大的肌肉量（力量 +6），但搬运它确实是个麻烦。"

#. ~ Description for HUGE_OK
#: .\mutations.json
msgid ""
"Your cardiovascular system has caught up with your muscular physique, so who"
" needs pathetic human cars? Strength +8."
msgstr "你的心血管系统已跟上你肌肉发达的体格，所以谁还需要可怜的人类汽车？力量 +8。"

#: .\mutations.json
msgid "Ratty Smarts"
msgstr "鼠辈智慧"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Ratty Smarts'}
#: .\mutations.json
msgid ""
"You bet that you could solve any maze or problem faster than those other "
"'survivors'.  +3 Intelligence"
msgstr "你打赌自己能比那些其他“幸存者”更快解决任何迷宫或问题。+3 智力"

#: .\mutations.json
msgid "Ratty Finesse"
msgstr "鼠辈灵巧"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Ratty Finesse'}
#: .\mutations.json
msgid ""
"Now the cataclysm is here it's better to be quick than slow.  +3 Dexterity"
msgstr "如今灾变降临，敏捷总比迟缓好。+3 敏捷"

#: .\mutations.json
msgid "No Ears"
msgstr "无耳"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'No Ears'}
#: .\mutations.json
msgid ""
"Your outer aural organs have disappeared leaving you without external ears "
"making you look a bit like a bird. This does not effect your hearing in any "
"way."
msgstr "你的外耳器官已消失，使你失去外耳，看起来有点像鸟类。这完全不影响你的听力。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'No Ears'}
#: .\mutations.json
msgid ""
"Your outer aural organs have disappeared leaving you without external ears "
"making you look a bit like a lizard. This does not effect your hearing in "
"any way."
msgstr "你的外耳器官已消失，使你失去外耳，看起来有点像蜥蜴。这完全不影响你的听力。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'No Ears'}
#: .\mutations.json
msgid ""
"Your outer aural organs have disappeared leaving you without external ears "
"making you look a bit like a raptor. This does not effect your hearing in "
"any way."
msgstr "你的外耳器官已消失，使你失去外耳，看起来有点像猛禽。这完全不影响你的听力。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'No Ears'}
#: .\mutations.json
msgid ""
"Your outer aural organs have disappeared leaving you without external ears "
"making you look a bit like a spider. This does not effect your hearing in "
"any way."
msgstr "你的外耳器官已消失，使你失去外耳，看起来有点像蜘蛛。这完全不影响你的听力。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'No Ears'}
#: .\mutations.json
msgid ""
"Your outer aural organs have disappeared leaving you without external ears "
"making you look a bit like some sort of insect. This does not effect your "
"hearing in any way."
msgstr "你的外耳器官已消失，使你失去外耳，看起来有点像某种昆虫。这完全不影响你的听力。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'No Ears'}
#: .\mutations.json
msgid ""
"Your outer aural organs have disappeared leaving you without external ears "
"making you look a bit like some sort of cephalopod. This does not effect "
"your hearing in any way."
msgstr "你的外耳器官已消失，使你失去外耳，看起来有点像某种头足类动物。这完全不影响你的听力。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'No Ears'}
#: .\mutations.json
msgid ""
"Your outer aural organs have disappeared leaving you without external ears "
"making you look a bit like a tortoise. This does not effect your hearing in "
"any way."
msgstr "你的外耳器官已消失，使你失去外耳，看起来有点像乌龟。这完全不影响你的听力。"

#: .\mutations.json
msgid "Fin Ears"
msgstr "鳍耳"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Fin Ears'}
#: .\mutations.json
msgid ""
"Your ears have changed into fin-like appendages. This does not effect your "
"hearing in any way but it does look striking. Slightly reduces wet effects"
msgstr "你的耳朵已变成鳍状附肢。这完全不影响你的听力，但看起来确实引人注目。略微减少潮湿效果"

#: .\mutations.json
msgid "No Nose"
msgstr "无鼻"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'No Nose'}
#: .\mutations.json
msgid ""
"Your entire nose has disappeared leaving nothing behind. This does not seem "
"to effect your sense of smell at all as you have developed other organs for "
"smell, but it does make you look rather inhuman."
msgstr "你的整个鼻子已消失，不留痕迹。这似乎完全不影响你的嗅觉，因为你已进化出其他嗅觉器官，但这让你看起来相当非人。"

#: .\mutations.json
msgid "Slit Nostrils"
msgstr "狭缝鼻孔"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Slit Nostrils'}
#: .\mutations.json
msgid ""
"You have a flattened nose and thin slits for nostrils, giving you a fish-"
"like appearance.  This makes breathing slightly difficult and increases "
"mouth encumbrance by 5."
msgstr "你有一个扁平的鼻子和细长的狭缝鼻孔，赋予你鱼类般的外观。这使呼吸略微困难，并增加 5 点口腔负重。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Slit Nostrils'}
#: .\mutations.json
msgid ""
"You have a flattened nose and thin slits for nostrils, giving you a "
"tortoise-like appearance.  This makes breathing slightly difficult and "
"increases mouth encumbrance by 5."
msgstr "你有一个扁平的鼻子和细长的狭缝鼻孔，赋予你龟类般的外观。这使呼吸略微困难，并增加 5 点口腔负重。"

#: .\mutations.json
msgid "Stinger"
msgstr "毒刺"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Stinger'}
#: .\mutations.json
msgid ""
"You have a bulbous bee-like abdomen tipped with a smooth stinger that bobs "
"behind you.  It does not improve your balance at all, but allows for a "
"powerful piercing attack.  Prevents wearing non-fabric pants."
msgstr "你有一个球根状的蜂类腹部，末端带有一根光滑的毒刺，在你身后摆动。它完全不会改善你的平衡，但允许进行强力的穿刺攻击。阻止穿着非织物裤子。"

#: .\mutations.json
msgid "You stab at %s with your insectoid stinger"
msgstr "你用你的昆虫毒刺刺向 %s"

#: .\mutations.json
msgid "%1$s stabs at %2$s with the insectoid stinger"
msgstr "%1$s 用昆虫毒刺刺向 %2$s"

#. ~ Description for TAIL_FIN
#: .\mutations.json
msgid ""
"You have a sleek, aquadynamic tail like that of a shark or dolphin. It "
"allows you to swim more quickly, but prevents wearing non-fabric pants.  "
"Slightly increases wet benefits."
msgstr "你有一条光滑、水动力学的尾巴，类似鲨鱼或海豚。它让你游得更快，但阻止穿着非织物裤子。略微增加潮湿增益。"

#: .\mutations.json
msgid "Fluffy Basher"
msgstr "蓬松重击者"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Fluffy Basher'}
#: .\mutations.json
msgid ""
"Your fluffy tail has now become pretty long and very strong... Possibly even"
" stronger than a baseball bat when its tensed, allowing for a mighty swing "
"attack. Great! you won't be needing a baseball bat anymore if you want to "
"play baseball and the funny part is that all the hits will be homerun! It "
"also has become a bit more controllable and prehensile."
msgstr ""
"你的蓬松尾巴现在变得相当长且非常强壮……紧绷时甚至可能比棒球棒更强，允许进行强力的挥击攻击。太棒了！如果你想打棒球，就不再需要棒球棒了，而且有趣的是所有击打都会是全垒打！它也变得更可控且更具抓握力。"

#: .\mutations.json
msgid "You strongly swing at %s with your mighty tail"
msgstr "你用你强壮的尾巴猛烈挥向 %s"

#: .\mutations.json
msgid "%1$s strongly swings at %2$s with its mighty tail"
msgstr "%1$s 用其强壮的尾巴猛烈挥向 %2$s"

#: .\mutations.json
msgid "Mutated Raptor Tail"
msgstr "突变猛禽尾"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Mutated Raptor Tail'}
#: .\mutations.json
msgid ""
"Your long semi-stiff lizard-like tail has mutated and now its slightly "
"longer and ends in a viciously sharp and boney point.  It does not improve "
"your balance at all, but allows you to lash with it and cause significant "
"piercing damage.  Prevents wearing non-fabric pants. Now that is a heavy "
"genetic modification."
msgstr ""
"你长长的半僵硬蜥蜴状尾巴已突变，现在它稍长一些，末端是一个恶毒尖锐的骨点。它完全不会改善你的平衡，但允许你用它抽打并造成显著的穿刺伤害。阻止穿着非织物裤子。这真是一个重大的基因改造。"

#: .\mutations.json
msgid "You stab %s with your tail"
msgstr "你用尾巴刺向 %s"

#: .\mutations.json
msgid "%1$s stabs %2$s with their tail"
msgstr "%1$s用尾巴刺向%2$s"

#: .\mutations.json
msgid "Razor Teeth"
msgstr "利齿"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Razor Teeth'}
#: .\mutations.json
msgid ""
"You have grown multiple rows of razor sharp teeth. They allow you to make a "
"super powerful bite attack, but they have caused your mouth and jaw to widen"
" significantly making you look like a shark or angler-fish"
msgstr "你长出了多排锋利的牙齿。它们让你能进行超级强力的撕咬攻击，但也导致你的嘴和下巴显著变宽，让你看起来像鲨鱼或琵琶鱼。"

#: .\mutations.json
msgid "You bite and tear into %s"
msgstr "你咬住并撕扯%s"

#: .\mutations.json
msgid "%1$s bites and tears into %2$s"
msgstr "%1$s咬住并撕扯%2$s"

#: .\mutations.json
msgid "Inconspicuous"
msgstr "不显眼"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Inconspicuous'}
#: .\mutations.json
msgid ""
"While sleeping or staying still, it is less likely that monsters will wander"
" close to you."
msgstr "在睡觉或保持静止时，怪物不太可能游荡到你附近。"

#: .\mutations.json
msgid "Webbed Extremities"
msgstr "蹼状四肢"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Webbed Extremities'}
#: .\mutations.json
msgid ""
"Your hands and feet are strongly webbed allowing you to swim much faster. "
"Unfortunately, gloves now give you problems and your dexterity is decreased "
"by 1. Slightly decreases wet penalties."
msgstr "你的手脚长出了强壮的蹼，让你能游得更快。不幸的是，现在戴手套会带来问题，并且你的敏捷度降低了1点。略微减少潮湿惩罚。"

#: .\mutations.json
msgid "Toe Roots"
msgstr "趾根"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Toe Roots'}
#: .\mutations.json
msgid ""
"Your toes have grown wriggly, and you can't imagine why you wear that stuff "
"on your feet.  Take it off.  It's in the way."
msgstr "你的脚趾变得蠕动扭曲，你无法想象为什么还要穿那些东西在脚上。脱掉它。它碍事了。"

#: .\mutations.json
msgid "Bony Scutes"
msgstr "骨质盾甲"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Bony Scutes'}
#: .\mutations.json
msgid ""
"A set of sub-dermal bony scutes has grown all over your body, giving you "
"something similar to an insect's exoskeleton. they give your scales a rough "
"and pebbly texture and are nigh impossible to penetrate. reduces wet "
"effects."
msgstr "一套皮下骨质盾甲遍布你的全身，赋予你类似昆虫外骨骼的结构。它们让你的鳞片呈现粗糙的鹅卵石质感，并且几乎无法穿透。减少潮湿效果。"

#: .\mutations.json
msgid "Tortoise Scales"
msgstr "龟甲鳞片"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Tortoise Scales'}
#: .\mutations.json
msgid ""
"A set of heavy, stiff, and thick scales has grown to cover your body, acting"
" as natural armor.  While very protective, it also severely limits your "
"flexibility, resulting in a -3 penalty to Dexterity.  Greatly reduces wet "
"effects."
msgstr ""
"一套沉重、僵硬且厚实的鳞片生长出来覆盖你的身体，充当天然护甲。虽然防护性极强，但也严重限制了你的灵活性，导致敏捷度受到-3惩罚。极大减少潮湿效果。"

#: .\mutations.json
msgid "Snapping Muzzle"
msgstr "啮咬口吻"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Snapping Muzzle'}
#: .\mutations.json
msgid ""
"Your face and jaws have morphed to look like those found on a snapping "
"turtle. It gives you a turtle-like look and they deliver a painful bite, but"
" prevent you from wearing mouthgear not made of fabric."
msgstr "你的脸和下巴变形，看起来像鳄龟的样子。这赋予你龟类的外观，并能进行痛苦的咬击，但阻止你佩戴非织物制成的口部装备。"

#: .\mutations.json
msgid "You snap at %s"
msgstr "你啮咬%s"

#: .\mutations.json
msgid "%1$s snaps at %2$s"
msgstr "%1$s啮咬%2$s"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Tortoise'}
#: .\mutations.json
msgid ""
"Now that you have your shell you can take your time with this survival "
"business."
msgstr "既然你有了自己的壳，你可以从容应对这场生存事业了。"

#: .\mutations.json
msgid "Bovine Eyes"
msgstr "牛眼"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Bovine Eyes'}
#: .\mutations.json
msgid ""
"Your eyes have mutated, now having a long and narrow horizontal pupil much "
"like those of a bovine.  This is visually striking, but it doesn't seem to "
"effect your vision at all."
msgstr "你的眼睛发生了突变，现在拥有细长的水平瞳孔，很像牛的眼睛。这在视觉上很引人注目，但似乎完全不影响你的视力。"

#: .\mutations.json
msgid "Arachnid Eyes"
msgstr "蛛形纲眼睛"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Arachnid Eyes'}
#: .\mutations.json
msgid ""
"You have grown 4 additional eyes and all of your eyes have become solid "
"pitch black. This increases your perception by 2 and makes you look more "
"spider-like."
msgstr "你长出了4只额外的眼睛，并且你所有的眼睛都变成了纯黑色。这使你的感知增加2点，并让你看起来更像蜘蛛。"

#: .\mutations.json
msgid "Tortoise Eyes"
msgstr "龟眼"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Tortoise Eyes'}
#: .\mutations.json
msgid ""
"Your eyes have mutated to resemble those found on a tortoise. This is "
"visually striking, but doesn't seem to affect your vision."
msgstr "你的眼睛突变得像龟的眼睛。这在视觉上很引人注目，但似乎不影响你的视力。"

#: .\mutations.json
msgid "Fishy Eyes"
msgstr "鱼眼"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Fishy Eyes'}
#: .\mutations.json
msgid ""
"Your eyes are now a solid black with no visible iris and barely noticeable "
"sclera. They give you a vaguely fish-like look but they otherwise serve no "
"purpose."
msgstr "你的眼睛现在变成了纯黑色，没有可见的虹膜，巩膜也几乎不明显。它们赋予你一种模糊的鱼类外观，但除此之外没有其他作用。"
